4.10	Ariane_Ascaride	Ariane Ascaride	Ariane Ascaride (born 10 October 1954, Marseille ) is a French actress and screenwriter. She has appeared in such films as Marius et Jeannette , Ma vraie vie à Rouen (The True Story of My Life in Rouen; USA, My Life on Ice) and À la place du coeur (Where the Heart Is). She also starred in and co-wrote the screenplay for Le Voyage en Arménie (Armenia).	http://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/e/e9/ASCARIDE_Ariane_03-24x30-2008b.jpg/220px-ASCARIDE_Ariane_03-24x30-2008b.jpg
